{"tid":2225450,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"二代美隊長展示「冇罪名」保釋紙：齋叫口號 國安法告唔入","createTime":"2020-10-01T10:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T12:30:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"865ddd52f122e81d510ca0453340f4843158adff","tid":2225450,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"網上有人號召參與今日10.1「月夕行動」，其中包括旺角MOKO商場。下午約3時，身穿黑衣、有「第二代美國隊長」之稱的馬先生現身，高叫「光復香港，時代革命」及「民族自強、香港獨立」等口號，不少現場市民和應，高叫「五大訴求 缺一不可」。<br />\n<br />\n馬先生展示3張保釋紙，指早前分別曾因涉嫌違反分裂國家罪、煽惑他人公眾妨擾罪和宣傳或公佈非法集會等三項罪名，但最後只有一宗繼續被控。他質疑單純叫口號，警方根本「告唔入」，故最終兩張保釋紙並無寫上任何罪名。他形容「港版國安法」尤如衝紅燈，認為如大家繼續叫相關口號、不自我噤聲，便不會有人因而被捕，「唔係叫句口號就分裂到國家」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/CCKSQQI7NJD6PLXWUO6XXQVXYA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FCCKSQQI7NJD6PLXWUO6XXQVXYA%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=db2b212b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FCCKSQQI7NJD6PLXWUO6XXQVXYA%2F&h=bf296075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/CCKSQQI7NJD6PLXWUO6XXQVXYA/</a>"},{"pid":"896864b952e4f9ccefeecafeca49d9a7b0bf331d","tid":2225450,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e4457199f382d5b2cf1855fab190ef6c55289c","tid":2225450,"uid":91397,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:38:18.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2397249d5dc51bd5b0e91083c7f769cd0df27290","tid":2225450,"uid":4239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/do